entries.content:
When user answers correctly, Colin MUST trigger unlock sequence:

1. ✅ Success Feedback (immediate)
2. 🎬 Door Opening Animation (2-3 seconds)
3. 🌟 Celebration Effect
4. 📊 Progress Update
5. ➡️ Transition to Next Level

---

## ANIMATION TEMPLATES BY THEME

### 🏰 HOGWARTS LIBRARY - Door Unlock
```html
<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto;">
    <!-- Success Banner -->
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #00ff88 100%);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.6);
    ">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #000;">
            ✅ CORRECT!
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; margin-top: 5px;">
            The magical seal breaks...
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Door Animation Container -->
    <div style="
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 350px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0033 0%, #2d1b4e 100%);
        border-radius: 15px;
        border: 3px solid #9d4edd;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(157,78,221,0.5);
    ">
        <!-- Magic Particles -->
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 20%; left: 10%; font-size: 20px; animation: float-away 2s ease-out; opacity: 0;">✨</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 30%; right: 15%; font-size: 18px; animation: float-away 2.2s ease-out; opacity: 0;">⭐</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 20%; font-size: 22px; animation: float-away 2.4s ease-out; opacity: 0;">💫</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 40%; right: 10%; font-size: 16px; animation: float-away 2.6s ease-out; opacity: 0;">✨</div>

        <!-- Left Door -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            top: 10%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 45%;
            height: 80%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a2c5e 0%, #2d1b4e 100%);
            border: 4px solid #9d4edd;
            border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;
            transform-origin: left center;
            animation: door-open-left 2s ease-out forwards;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        ">
            <!-- Door Rune -->
            <div style="
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                right: 20px;
                transform: translateY(-50%);
                font-size: 40px;
                animation: rune-fade 1.5s ease-out;
                opacity: 0;
            ">🔮</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Door -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            top: 10%;
            left: 5%;
            width: 45%;
            height: 80%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d1b4e 0%, #4a2c5e 100%);
            border: 4px solid #9d4edd;
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
            transform-origin: right center;
            animation: door-open-right 2s ease-out forwards;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        ">
            <!-- Door Rune -->
            <div style="
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                left: 20px;
                transform: translateY(-50%);
                font-size: 40px;
                animation: rune-fade 1.5s ease-out;
                opacity: 0;
            ">🔮</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Light Burst Behind Door -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(157,78,221,0.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: light-burst 2s ease-out;
            opacity: 0;
        "></div>

        <!-- Next Level Preview -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fade-in-delayed 2s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        ">
            <div style="font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 10px;">📜</div>
            <div style="color: #e0aaff; font-size: 16px; font-family: Georgia, serif;">
                Next Chamber Awaits...
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Collected -->
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        animation: bounce-in 1s ease-out 1.5s backwards;
    ">
        <div style="
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700 0%, #ffed4e 100%);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.5);
        ">
            <span style="font-size: 30px;">🔑</span>
            <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #000; margin-left: 10px;">
                KEY OBTAINED
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
@keyframes slideDown {
    from { transform: translateY(-50px); opacity: 0; }
    to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes door-open-left {
    0% { transform: perspective(1200px) rotateY(0deg); }
    100% { transform: perspective(1200px) rotateY(-120deg); }
}

@keyframes door-open-right {
    0% { transform: perspective(1200px) rotateY(0deg); }
    100% { transform: perspective(1200px) rotateY(120deg); }
}

@keyframes rune-fade {
    0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.5); }
}

@keyframes light-burst {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.5); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.5); }
}

@keyframes float-away {
    0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-100px) scale(1.5); }
}

@keyframes fade-in-delayed {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.8); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
}

@keyframes bounce-in {
    0% { transform: scale(0) translateY(50px); opacity: 0; }
    60% { transform: scale(1.1) translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scale(1) translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
}
</style>
```

---

### 🏛️ EGYPTIAN TOMB - Stone Door Slide
```html
<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto;">
    <!-- Success Banner -->
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d4a373 0%, #ffd700 100%);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212,163,115,0.6);
    ">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1506;">
            ✅ CORRECT!
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #3d2a0f; margin-top: 5px;">
            The ancient mechanism activates...
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Door Animation Container -->
    <div style="
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 350px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1506 0%, #3d2a0f 100%);
        border-radius: 15px;
        border: 3px solid #d4a373;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(212,163,115,0.5);
    ">
        <!-- Sand Particles -->
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 50%; width: 100px; height: 2px; background: rgba(193,154,107,0.6); animation: sand-fall-1 2s ease-out;"></div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 30%; width: 80px; height: 2px; background: rgba(193,154,107,0.4); animation: sand-fall-2 2.2s ease-out;"></div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 10%; left: 70%; width: 60px; height: 2px; background: rgba(193,154,107,0.3); animation: sand-fall-3 2.4s ease-out;"></div>

        <!-- Stone Door (slides up) -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 5%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 70%;
            height: 85%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a4a3a 0%, #3d2a0f 100%);
            border: 5px solid #d4a373;
            border-radius: 5px;
            animation: stone-slide-up 2.5s ease-out forwards;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        ">
            <!-- Hieroglyphs Glow -->
            <div style="
                position: absolute;
                top: 30%;
                left: 50%;
                transform: translateX(-50%);
                font-size: 24px;
                color: #d4a373;
                text-shadow: 0 0 20px #d4a373;
                animation: hieroglyph-glow 1.5s ease-out;
            ">
                ⵌⴰⵏⴰⵡⴰⵢ<br>
                ⵜⵉⴼⵉⵏⴰⵖ
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Golden Light Behind -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60%;
            height: 80%;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, rgba(255,215,0,0.6) 0%, transparent 60%);
            animation: golden-glow 2.5s ease-out;
            opacity: 0;
        "></div>

        <!-- Next Chamber Symbol -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fade-in-delayed 2.5s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        ">
            <div style="font-size: 60px; margin-bottom: 10px;">🏺</div>
            <div style="color: #f4e4c1; font-size: 16px; font-family: Palatino, serif;">
                The Path Opens...
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dust Clouds -->
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 5%; left: 20%; width: 100px; height: 50px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(193,154,107,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%); animation: dust-cloud-1 2s ease-out;"></div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 5%; right: 20%; width: 120px; height: 60px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(193,154,107,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%); animation: dust-cloud-2 2.2s ease-out;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scarab Collected -->
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        animation: bounce-in 1s ease-out 2s backwards;
    ">
        <div style="
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700 0%, #d4a373 100%);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.5);
        ">
            <span style="font-size: 30px;">🪲</span>
            <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1506; margin-left: 10px;">
                SCARAB KEY OBTAINED
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
@keyframes stone-slide-up {
    0% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-110%); }
}

@keyframes golden-glow {
    0% { opacity: 0; }
    40% { opacity: 1; }
    100% { opacity: 0.6; }
}

@keyframes hieroglyph-glow {
    0% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px #d4a373; opacity: 1; }
    100% { text-shadow: 0 0 50px #ffd700; opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes sand-fall-1 {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: translateY(300px); opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes sand-fall-2 {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { transform: translateY(320px); opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes sand-fall-3 {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.3; }
    100% { transform: translateY(340px); opacity: 0; }
}

@keyframes dust-cloud-1 {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(1.5); }
}

@keyframes dust-cloud-2 {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(1.5); }
}
</style>
```

