### 🛸 CYBER SPACE STATION - Iris Door
```html
<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto;">
    <!-- Success Banner -->
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff 0%, #00ff88 100%);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,255,0.8);
    ">
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #000; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
            ✅ ACCESS GRANTED
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #0a0e27; margin-top: 5px;">
            Opening iris portal...
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Door Animation Container -->
    <div style="
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 350px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0e27 0%, #1a1f3a 100%);
