## 🎉 最终关卡胜利动画

### World Info Entry: Victory Sequence

**Entry Name:** `Final Victory Animation`  
**Keywords:** `final level`, `最后一关`, `victory`, `胜利`, `escape success`  
**Priority:** 100

**Content:**
```html
<div style="position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 700px; margin: 40px auto; text-align: center;">
    <!-- Fireworks Background -->
    <div style="
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 1000;
    ">
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 20%; left: 20%; font-size: 40px; animation: firework-1 2s ease-out infinite;">🎆</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 30%; right: 15%; font-size: 50px; animation: firework-2 2.5s ease-out infinite;">✨</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 10%; font-size: 45px; animation: firework-3 3s ease-out infinite;">🎇</div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 40%; right: 25%; font-size: 35px; animation: firework-4 2.8s ease-out infinite;">💫</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Victory Banner -->
    <div style="
        background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffd700 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        animation: victory-zoom 1s ease-out;
        box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,215,0,0.8);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    ">
        <!-- Shimmer Effect -->
        <div style="
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 50%, transparent 70%);
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
        "></div>

        <div style="position: relative; z-index: 2;">
            <div style="font-size: 60px; margin-bottom: 15px; animation: bounce-celebration 1s ease-out infinite;">
                🏆
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; color: #000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); margin-bottom: 10px;">
                ESCAPE SUCCESSFUL!
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 18px; color: #1a0033;">
                All knowledge points mastered ✨
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Panel -->
    <div style="
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29 0%, #302b63 100%);
        border: 3px solid #ffd700;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        animation: slide-up 1s ease-out 0.5s backwards;
    ">
        <div style="color: #ffd700; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            📊 MISSION COMPLETE
        </div>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; color: #fff;">
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;">Total Levels</div>
                <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #00d4ff;">{{总关卡数}}</div>
            </div>

            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;">Keys Collected</div>
                <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffd700;">{{总关卡数}}/{{总关卡数}}</div>
            </div>

            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;">Accuracy</div>
                <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #00ff88;">{{准确率}}%</div>
            </div>

            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px;">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa;">Time Spent</div>
                <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #ff6b6b;">{{耗时}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Knowledge Summary -->
    <div style="
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        border: 2px solid #00d4ff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        animation: fade-in 1.5s ease-out 1s backwards;
    ">
        <div style="color: #00d4ff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            ✅ KNOWLEDGE POINTS MASTERED
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: left; color: #fff; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2;">
            {{列出所有已掌握的规则，每条前面加✓}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Achievement Badge -->
    <div style="
        animation: rotate-badge 2s ease-out 1.5s backwards;
